    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This beauty is in absolute mint condition and has been my pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied it since day one\u2014always garaged and kept spotless. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person! If you want a top-tier car without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 45500.0,
