    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a concours-level specimen featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power up to an 8,400 RPM redline via eight individual throttle bodies. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission, this unit retains its factory carbon fiber roof to maintain a low center of gravity. The vehicle is mechanically superlative, with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator servicing already performed. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring telepathic turn-in and optimal traction. With a pristine undercarriage and flawless paint depth, this is a collector-grade example of BMW's final high-revving V8 masterpiece.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
